{
  "stem": "27770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took probably two cans in a gas chamber went, each time when they gassed people, 1,500 people went to one gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was next to the gas chamber eight months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew the whole story what goes on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I arrived to Auschwitz, the first half an hour I knew everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Probably you could ask me why do I know and the rest they don't know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When they made the selection when we arrived, also we arrived to Auschwitz around 4-- 3:00, halfway dark, the minute they opened up, those gangsters, the doors from the trains, right away barking doors-- dogs.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "SS rush.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] Fast.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] Go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you was mixed up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Should you look for you sister?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Should you look for the package?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Should you look for your relatives?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Should you look for your older man?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First one, two, three, down from the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Jewish-- Polish Jewish people who were there already many years, their work was to make it fast of the work, and they had also uniforms, these striped suits, and what they did, they tried-- they tried to save as much as they could by doing it, take away from the mother's hand, this baby, and give it right away over to an older person, to his mother, to his father.",
      "word_count": 72
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She should not, when it comes to the selection, because any minute started the selection.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here the man, here the woman, here you go right, here you go left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were screaming that they are-- they are gangsters, those Jewish, why?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You took away my child.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
